Chipotle-Style Beef Burrito

$12.99
850 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

DairySoy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten-Free

Tags:

BurritoMexican CuisineBeefGluten-Free

Description

A hearty burrito filled with succulent beef, zesty salsa, and creamy guacamole wrapped in a gluten-free tortilla.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 1 lb
  • Gluten-Free Tortilla: 2 large
  • Black Beans: 1 cup
  • Corn: 1 cup
  • Sour Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Guacamole: 1/2 cup
  • Shredded Cheese: 1 cup
  • Salsa: 1 cup
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • Lime Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Spices (Cumin, Paprika, Chili Powder): to taste
